dct_title_s: Syria : discover Syria / digital cartography GEOprojects (UK) Ltd. (Verso)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by gradient tints and spot heights. Panel title. At head of panel title: GEOprojects Arab World Map Library. Includes 3 ancillary maps of Palmyra, Damascus, and Aleppo, index for Syria map, street indexes for Damascus and Aleppo maps, business guide, information on the Syrian Arab Republic, and color illustrations. Ancillary map of Palmyra (Tadmor) at 1:10,000 on recto. Ancillary maps of Damascus (Esh Sham) at 1:15,000 and Aleppo (Halab) at 1:12,500, business guide, and color illustrations on verso.
dct_publisher_sm: Reading, UK : GEOprojects (UK) Ltd. ; Beirut, Lebanon : GEOprojects s.a.r.l., c2014.
